---
title: Spicy Bibimbap-Style Shrimp and Rice Bowls with Beyond Meat®, Zucchini and Carrots
description: Our take on the Korean rice bowl is packed with veggies, rice and Beyond Meat®. Finish it with a spicy-sweet sesame sauce, then stir all these vibrant ingredients together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-riz-et-de-crevettes-epices-style-bibimbap-260f49c5.jpg
